WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:16.000
The Magic Barber by John Millen

00:16.000 --> 00:20.000
It is afternoon in crossways.

00:20.000 --> 00:23.000
Crossways is a quiet town.

00:23.000 --> 00:27.000
Crossways is a sleepy town.

00:27.000 --> 00:31.000
Everybody in crossways wears a large hat.

00:31.000 --> 00:36.000
Everybody in crossways wears a black hat.

00:36.000 --> 00:41.000
The women wear round black hats.

00:41.000 --> 00:44.000
The men wear tall black hats.

00:44.000 --> 00:48.000
The girls wear square black hats.

00:48.000 --> 00:53.000
The boys wear flat black hats.

00:53.000 --> 00:56.000
Everybody has long hair.

00:56.000 --> 01:01.000
Everybody wears a large hat.

01:01.000 --> 01:08.000
Everybody wears a large hat over their long hair.

01:08.000 --> 01:11.000
It is afternoon in crossways.

01:11.000 --> 01:14.000
The sun is shining brightly.

01:14.000 --> 01:17.000
It is a hot afternoon.

01:17.000 --> 01:20.000
Everybody is sleeping.

01:20.000 --> 01:24.000
Suddenly there is a loud noise.

01:24.000 --> 01:26.000
Everybody wakes up.

01:26.000 --> 01:29.000
They all look round.

01:29.000 --> 01:31.000
What is happening?

01:31.000 --> 01:35.000
Who is making that loud noise?

01:35.000 --> 01:40.000
A small boy is walking along the street.

01:40.000 --> 01:43.000
He is beating a drum.

01:43.000 --> 01:48.000
The small boy is walking in front of a donkey.

01:48.000 --> 01:52.000
The donkey is pulling a cart.

01:52.000 --> 01:55.000
A man is sitting on the cart.

01:55.000 --> 01:59.000
There is a large notice above the man's head.

01:59.000 --> 02:01.000
The Magic Barber.

02:01.000 --> 02:03.000
Why wear hats?

02:03.000 --> 02:06.000
Have your hair cut all shapes.

02:06.000 --> 02:08.000
All colors.

02:08.000 --> 02:10.000
Only one dollar.

02:10.000 --> 02:13.000
Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!

02:13.000 --> 02:16.000
Everybody reads the notice.

02:16.000 --> 02:20.000
Everybody in crossways is happy.

02:20.000 --> 02:22.000
They don't like black hats.

02:22.000 --> 02:26.000
They don't want to wear hats anymore.

02:26.000 --> 02:29.000
They all shout and cheer.

02:29.000 --> 02:38.000
Hurry! Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!

02:38.000 --> 02:43.000
They all throw their hats in the air.

02:43.000 --> 02:47.000
The wind blows the hats high in the sky.

02:47.000 --> 02:50.000
They all cheer and shout.

02:50.000 --> 02:55.000
Goodbye hats! Goodbye hats!

02:55.000 --> 02:58.000
Nobody sees the small boy.

02:58.000 --> 03:00.000
He is busy.

03:00.000 --> 03:04.000
He is picking up the hats.

03:04.000 --> 03:10.000
The small boy is putting the hats into a large bag.

03:10.000 --> 03:16.000
He fills the large bag with the hats.

03:16.000 --> 03:20.000
The small boy lifts up the large bag.

03:20.000 --> 03:23.000
He runs out of the town.

03:23.000 --> 03:28.000
He is carrying the large bag on his back.

03:32.000 --> 03:36.000
A young man climbs onto the cart.

03:36.000 --> 03:39.000
He sits down on the chair.

03:39.000 --> 03:42.000
He pays the barber a dollar.

03:42.000 --> 03:49.000
The magic barber puts a large white towel over the young man's head.

03:49.000 --> 03:54.000
He waves a large pair of scissors in the air.

03:54.000 --> 03:57.000
He shouts the magic words.

03:57.000 --> 04:04.000
Snip, snip, up and down, round and round and off it comes.

04:04.000 --> 04:08.000
The magic barber pulls away the towel.

04:08.000 --> 04:11.000
Everybody shouts.

04:11.000 --> 04:14.000
The young man's hair is short.

04:14.000 --> 04:19.000
The young man's hair is green.

04:19.000 --> 04:22.000
Everybody shouts and cheers.

04:22.000 --> 04:25.000
Everybody is happy.

04:25.000 --> 04:27.000
Yeah!

04:32.000 --> 04:36.000
The magic barber cuts everybody's hair.

04:36.000 --> 04:39.000
The women have blue hair.

04:39.000 --> 04:42.000
The men have green hair.

04:42.000 --> 04:45.000
The boys have red hair.

04:45.000 --> 04:48.000
The girls have yellow hair.

04:48.000 --> 04:54.000
Nobody in crossways is wearing a hat.

04:56.000 --> 05:00.000
The people of crossways go to bed.

05:00.000 --> 05:03.000
They wake up in the morning.

05:03.000 --> 05:06.000
A young man looks in the mirror.

05:06.000 --> 05:08.000
What has happened?

05:08.000 --> 05:10.000
Where is his hair?

05:10.000 --> 05:13.000
He has no hair.

05:13.000 --> 05:16.000
He is bald.

05:18.000 --> 05:22.000
The people of crossways are angry.

05:22.000 --> 05:24.000
Everybody is bald.

05:24.000 --> 05:27.000
They have no hair.

05:27.000 --> 05:30.000
They want their hats back.

05:30.000 --> 05:32.000
Where is my hat?

05:32.000 --> 05:35.000
I want my hat back.

05:43.000 --> 05:46.000
Suddenly there is a loud noise.

05:46.000 --> 05:50.000
A small boy is walking along the street.

05:50.000 --> 05:53.000
He is blowing a trumpet.

05:53.000 --> 05:56.000
He is blowing the trumpet loudly.

06:03.000 --> 06:08.000
The small boy is walking in front of a donkey.

06:08.000 --> 06:11.000
The donkey is pulling a cart.

06:11.000 --> 06:15.000
A man is sitting on the cart.

06:15.000 --> 06:19.000
The cart is full of black hats.

06:19.000 --> 06:23.000
There is a notice above the cart.

06:23.000 --> 06:26.000
Everybody reads the notice.

06:26.000 --> 06:29.000
They cheer and shout.

06:30.000 --> 06:33.000
Everybody buys a black hat.

06:33.000 --> 06:37.000
The black hats cover their bald heads.

06:37.000 --> 06:40.000
Everybody is happy.

06:40.000 --> 06:42.000
Hats for sale.

06:42.000 --> 06:45.000
All shapes, all sizes.

06:45.000 --> 06:48.000
Only two dollars.

